**Staging Systems:**

**Revised ASRM Stages (1996):**

| Stage | Description | Location |
|-------|-------------|
| I | Minimal | Superficial peritoneal implants |
| II | Mild | Some deeper implants |
| III | Moderate | Deep implants with adhesions |
| IV | Severe | Endometriomas present |

**Enzian Classification:**

| Stage | Implants | Description |
|-------|----------|-------------|
| I | Minimal | Small, superficial implants |
| II | Mild | Some deeper implants |
| III | Moderate | Deep implants with adhesions |
| IV | Severe | Endometriomas present |

